snippet.title: Ranma (七笑拳), 1990, DOS, Action, SoftStar
snippet.description: Interesting gameplay genre mix from oldest Taiwan developers - SoftStar. This game includes following genres: platformer, fighting and turn-based first-person adventure located in dungeon-crawler setting. The game based on the Japanese manga and TV-series - “Ranma1/2”.
